      <title>马士基警告南非沿海地区极端天气可能导致延误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/maersk-warns-of-extreme-weather-delays-along-south-african-coast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[A.P. 穆勒-马士基集团警告称，极端天气条件和袭击南非海岸的风暴潮预计将造成航运延误。]]></description>
