    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚航空取消航班 数千人滞留罗马尼亚机场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/thousands-stranded-at-romanian-airport-as-tarom-cancels-flights</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚国有航空公司 Tarom 因缺少机组人员于周一取消了约 20 个航班，导致包括政府官员在内的数千人被困在布加勒斯特机场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/thousands-stranded-at-romanian-airport-as-tarom-cancels-flights</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:12:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国实施新制度导致尾盘交易韩元流动性下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/won-liquidity-drops-for-late-trades-as-korea-debuts-new-regime</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在韩元延长交易的第一周深夜时段，韩元的流动性出现下降，这对那些热衷于提振市场的官员来说是一个潜在的挫折，并且在全球投资者获得更多渠道之际，加大了价格大幅波动的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/won-liquidity-drops-for-late-trades-as-korea-debuts-new-regime</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>预算缺口扩大，匈牙利提高银行暴利税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/hungary-raises-windfall-taxes-on-banks-to-plug-budget-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利宣布对银行征收新税，并取消了削减针对目标行业的暴利税的计划，因为新数据显示预算赤字进一步扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/hungary-raises-windfall-taxes-on-banks-to-plug-budget-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 08:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大选后谨慎买家涌现，法国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国股市上涨，扭转了早盘的跌势，因为在左翼政党意外获胜、议会出现分裂且没有明显多数的情况下，投资者将选举结果视为“最不坏”的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Grifols 称创始家族和 Brookfield 正在考虑收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/grifols-family-brookfield-reported-in-talks-to-bid-for-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基立福制药公司 (Grifols SA) 表示，在遭到做空者的攻击导致这家制药商市值缩水数十亿美元后，其创始家族和资产管理公司 Brookfield 已提出收购并将其摘牌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/grifols-family-brookfield-reported-in-talks-to-bid-for-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 05:59:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币的 Mt. Gox 波动进一步表明加密货币反弹艰难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/bitcoin-btc-drops-anew-on-fears-of-sales-from-mt-gox-distributions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心破产的 Mt. Gox 交易所的债权人可能出售比特币，比特币价格再次下跌，这加剧了人们对始于去年的加密货币牛市是否还能保持动力的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/bitcoin-btc-drops-anew-on-fears-of-sales-from-mt-gox-distributions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 01:35:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者评估生产风险，油价小幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在上周触及两个月高点后小幅走低，尽管交易商追踪美国飓风和加拿大野火对原油生产构成的双重威胁，但近期涨势仍有所降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 23:29:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
